    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要么发财要么死！《Supernatural Squad》是一款恐怖又欢乐的多人合作冒险游戏，你将和好友组队前往危险的古代遗迹，对付恐怖的远古怪物，拿走珍贵的宝藏。这本【超自然生存指南】请收好，祝你寻宝之旅愉快，早日发财。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/4bf589c4f01a4279d3b5af94089dd8e8.poster.avif?t=1737631704\" width=594 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/4bf589c4f01a4279d3b5af94089dd8e8.webm?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/4bf589c4f01a4279d3b5af94089dd8e8.mp4?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1.探险目标</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他三位朋友组建冒险小队，前往未知的神秘古迹，收集奇珍异宝，把这些宝贝带回来走向发财之路，并不断升级装备向更危险的遗迹进发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/af77529388f67958ec8e339321ce4bae.poster.avif?t=1737631704\" width=594 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/af77529388f67958ec8e339321ce4bae.webm?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/af77529388f67958ec8e339321ce4bae.mp4?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2.活下去！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将会遇到鬼新娘、提线木偶等恐怖惊悚的远古怪物、险象环生的陷阱，甚至迷失在错综复杂的迷宫之中！每一步都可能是你冒险的终点，所以请利用好你的生存道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/56d1ed912d6e1d0f36dd9b381e7c55e6.poster.avif?t=1737631704\" width=594 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/56d1ed912d6e1d0f36dd9b381e7c55e6.webm?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/56d1ed912d6e1d0f36dd9b381e7c55e6.mp4?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3.合作共赢</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的队友多多配合，共同克服难关，在天黑之前带着宝物回来。不过小心，别把伪人当成队友，也别被个别猪队友坑了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/378426572b3d8d5af4283fd36782019e.poster.avif?t=1737631704\" width=594 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/378426572b3d8d5af4283fd36782019e.webm?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/378426572b3d8d5af4283fd36782019e.mp4?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏包含以下内容：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四名玩家在线合作 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时语音聊天</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐怖的远古怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好友见鬼时的窘态</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔性互动舞蹈</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超多有用的道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >历史悠久的神秘宝藏</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/293c6f0541d587c75b3ce2b745b4b279.poster.avif?t=1737631704\" width=594 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/293c6f0541d587c75b3ce2b745b4b279.webm?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302740/extras/293c6f0541d587c75b3ce2b745b4b279.mp4?t=1737631704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你探险愉快，活着回来！</p>",
